_header: There was cast a stone that no man might lift

OxfMert248.Transcription:
þer was kast a ston þat no man miȝte lefteþer was
                    knigt a knotte þat noman miȝte vn knetteþer was ytamed a
                    best þat noman miȝte wiþ sette
OxfMert248.Note:
Added to lower margin of page; ‘A’ precedes each of first
                    two lines.
